#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:1
msgid "Deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:3
msgid ""
"The CPRMV API runs as a Docker container. The image is built and pushed by "
"GitLab CI to Docker Hub (`datafluisteraar/cprmv-api`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:7
msgid "Docker image"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:9
msgid "The `serve_api/Dockerfile` builds from `python:3.12-bookworm`:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:11
msgid "Installs `nl_NL.UTF-8` locale."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:12
msgid "Copies `src/`, `data/`, and `respec/` into the image."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:13
msgid "Creates a non-root `appuser` for security."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:14
msgid "Exposes port `8000`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:15
msgid ""
"Health check via `urllib.request.urlopen('http://localhost:8000/', timeout=5)"
"`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:16
msgid "Entrypoint: `fastapi run src/serve.py --port 8000 --host 0.0.0.0`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:20
msgid "Running with Docker Compose"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:22
msgid ""
"`serve_api/docker-compose.yml` provides a production-ready configuration:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:24
msgid ""
"services:\n"
"  cprmv-api:\n"
"    image: datafluisteraar/cprmv-api:${IMAGE_TAG:-latest}\n"
"    ports:\n"
"      - \"8000:8000\"\n"
"    volumes:\n"
"      - ./data:/app/data\n"
"    restart: unless-stopped\n"
"    environment:\n"
"      - PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:37
msgid ""
"The `data/` volume mount allows updating the XSLT files and method TTLs "
"without rebuilding the image."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:39
msgid "**Start:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:41
msgid "docker compose up -d"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:45
msgid "**Use a specific image version:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:47
msgid "IMAGE_TAG=abc1234 docker compose up -d"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:51
msgid "**Logs:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:53
msgid "docker compose logs -f cprmv-api"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:57
msgid "**Stop:**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:59
msgid "docker compose down"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:65
msgid "Synology NAS deployment"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:67
msgid ""
"The original deployment target documented in `serve_api/README.md` is a "
"Synology NAS:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:69
msgid ""
"# Build locally\n"
"cd /volume2/development/cprmv/serve-api/\n"
"docker build -t cprmv-fastapi .\n"
"\n"
"# Run\n"
"docker run -d --name cprmv-api -p 8000:8000 cprmv-fastapi"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:78
msgid ""
"On Synology, the data volume should be mounted from `/volume2/docker/cprmv/`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:82
msgid "Updating to a new image version"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:84
msgid "After CI pushes a new image to Docker Hub:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:86
msgid ""
"docker compose pull\n"
"docker compose up -d"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:91
msgid ""
"The `IMAGE_TAG` environment variable can pin to a specific commit SHA from "
"the CI build output."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:95
msgid "Health check"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cprmv-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:97
msgid ""
"The container's built-in health check polls `http://localhost:8000/` every "
"30 seconds with a 30-second timeout, 3 retries, and a 5-second start period. "
"The `/` endpoint returns `{\"CPRMV Rules Serve API\": \"0.4.0\"}`."
msgstr ""

